OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLight winds
OL,6,Fat first with low cloud and coastal
OL,7,Fmist again spilling inland from the
OL,8,FNorth Sea. Staying dry, although winds
OL,9,Fstrengthening around the coasts a
OL,10,Flittle by dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloud clearing to the coasts
OL,13,Fthrough the morning, to give good
OL,14,Fsunny spells further inland. Perhaps
OL,15,Ffeeling a little cooler due to a
OL,16,Ffresher north to northeasterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
